description:
The EASI scoring system uses a defined process to grade the severity of the 
 signs of eczema and the extent affected.
name: Eczema Area and Severity Index (EASI) Score

#head_neck_indicator.heading: Remember: Include only inflamed areas in your assessment; do not include xerosis (dryness), ichthyosis, keratosis pilaris, urticaria, infection (unless there is underlying eczema), or post inflammatory pigmentation changes.
